[Corvus3]
Say=I have to ride out immediately on a raid with General Ovoron.  We were waiting to see if the supply fleet could make it through the blockade before we took the risk, but since the Lady Aele was the only one to make it through, it seems that we must indeed resort to more drastic measures.
