[Corvus4]
Say=Slow down, little brother.  Horses are in short supply and we need to move fast tonight.  I've pulled some strings and obtained a commission for you, but that's all our family name will get you here.  You will have to prove yourself to General Roth and Captain Calvaric on your own before it will be anything more than a piece of paper.
RspDflt=none
RspTxt1=So I am forced to wait here uselessly until your return, then?
nxtln1=corvus6

[Corvus6]
